title: Change Linux User's Uid (User Id)
tags: @zettel _method linux
roam-id: 5f1fa056-f90a-449d-8571-0056bdb96a2b
type: text/markdown

I\'ll set my user id from 1000 to 666

``` shell
# login as root to your machine (ssh or tty4)
getent passwd 666 # make sure the user id is not in use by others
usermode -u 666 savolla
find / -user 1000 -exec chown -h 666 {} \; # fix permissions for savolla
reboot
```
